server_start_failed.description:
The ESPHome MCP server could not be started inside Home Assistant:

{detail}

Check the Home Assistant logs, then reload the integration to retry.

server_package_import_failed.description:
Importing a dependency for the ESPHome MCP server failed:

{detail}

Check the Home Assistant logs and reload the integration to retry.

server_restart_required.description:
ESPHome MCP protected a shared Python dependency from being replaced while Home Assistant was running:

{detail}

Update ESPHome MCP and ha-mcp to compatible versions, then restart Home Assistant.
